text.tspan: Put circle in all boxes as you read the instruction.

flowRoot.flowPara: When finished, put circle in box and change sheet.

tspan.style: font-size:18px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:bold;font-stretch:normal;text-align:start;line-height:150%;writing-mode:lr-tb;text-anchor:start;font-family:Arial Rounded MT Bold;-inkscape-font-specification:'Arial Rounded MT Bold, Bold'

text.tspan: Connect same shapes from column A to column F by lines. Please use pen with no ink.

tspan.style: font-size:18px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:bold;font-stretch:normal;text-align:start;line-height:150%;writing-mode:lr-tb;text-anchor:start;font-family:Arial Rounded MT Bold;-inkscape-font-specification:'Arial Rounded MT Bold, Bold'

text.tspan: Start at A1 and make 5 connections until you reach column F. Connect all same shapes irrespective of rotation.

tspan.style: font-size:18px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:bold;font-stretch:normal;text-align:start;line-height:150%;writing-mode:lr-tb;text-anchor:start;font-family:Arial Rounded MT Bold;-inkscape-font-specification:'Arial Rounded MT Bold, Bold'

text.tspan: Make 5 such paths starting also at A2, A3, A4 and A5 stopping at column F. An example is shown in the right panel.
